OL,3,CBride-to-be to take bus to own wedding
OL,4,Cdue to lack of accessible transport
OL,6,FIt's wedding season ` a time when many
OL,7,Fwill be preparing for the happiest day
OL,8,Fof their life ` but, for disabled
OL,9,Fpeople, there can be additional
OL,10,Fchallenges to overcome just to get to
OL,11,Fthe wedding venue.
OL,13,FSarah Tunnicliffe, from Cardiff, has
OL,14,Flimb-girdle muscular dystrophy - a
OL,15,Frare genetic disease that causes
OL,16,Fprogressive muscle weakness - and uses
OL,17,Fa powered wheelchair. She says the
OL,18,Fprocess of preparing for her wedding
OL,19,Fat the end of August has been a very
OL,20,Fdifferent one to other brides-to-be.
