OL,3,CBride-to-be to take bus to own wedding
OL,4,Cdue to lack of accessible transport
OL,6,F"As a young girl, I always imagined
OL,7,Fwhat a wedding, and the experiences
OL,8,Fthat go with it, would look like; but
OL,9,Fthat's something that, from my
OL,10,Fperspective, feels a bit different in
OL,11,Fthis situation. I've had a few
OL,12,Fchallenges along the way."
