OL,3,CBride-to-be to take bus to own wedding
OL,4,Cdue to lack of accessible transport
OL,6,FThe main challenge she's faced is
OL,7,Ffinding accessible transport. Sarah
OL,8,Fand her fiance, Jamie, live in
OL,9,FAdamsdown, Cardiff. They're getting
OL,10,Fmarried a mile and a half away, at the
OL,11,FRoyal Welsh College of Music and
OL,12,FDrama, but Sarah says she's been
OL,13,Funable to find an adequate vehicle to
OL,14,Ftake her there.
OL,26,@pD@Nrr
