OL,3,CBride-to-be to take bus to own wedding
OL,4,Cdue to lack of accessible transport
OL,6,F"I've looked at private hire of
OL,7,Fwheelchair-accessible vehicles;
OL,8,Fhowever, availability is few and far
OL,9,Fbetween, and the cost is in excess of
OL,10,F#600 when we only want it for maybe
OL,11,Fhalf an hour of the day. The other
OL,12,Foptions are taxis, but some are just
OL,13,Fthat little bit too small for my
OL,14,Fwheelchair. I would just like to have
OL,15,Fthat little bit of extra comfort on my
OL,16,Fwedding day and to not worry about my
OL,17,Fdress being crumpled up against the
OL,18,Ffolded-down seats."
