OL,3,CBride-to-be to take bus to own wedding
OL,4,Cdue to lack of accessible transport
OL,6,FNHS worker Sarah says she's contacted
OL,7,Fprivate companies and made enquiries
OL,8,Fabout short-term rentals in Cardiff,
OL,9,FSwansea, Newport, as well as over the
OL,10,Fborder in England; but she says she's
OL,11,Feither been told there are no suitable
OL,12,Fvehicles available or hasn't received
OL,13,Fa response.
OL,15,F"It means I have to do more, but how
OL,16,Fmany times can I be told no? It's a
OL,17,Fchallenge and it's something that's
OL,18,Ftaken up a lot of time and energy.
OL,19,FIt's mentally exhausting. It shouldn't
OL,20,Fbe that hard."
