OL,3,CBride-to-be to take bus to own wedding
OL,4,Cdue to lack of accessible transport
OL,6,FAs things stand, Sarah will be relying
OL,7,Fon the capital city's public transport
OL,8,Fto get her and her 270kg chair to the
OL,9,Fvenue on time by catching a bus not
OL,10,Ffar from her doorstep.
OL,12,F"This is the choice I've made. It's
OL,13,Ffrustrating, it's disappointing;
OL,14,Fhowever, I'd rather feel those
OL,15,Femotions today than on the morning of
OL,16,Fmy wedding day. The bus will be my
OL,17,Fcarriage!"
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@JO]
