OL,4,Cdue to lack of accessible transport
OL,6,FJust over a third of disabled people
OL,7,Fin Wales are married (34.1%, 2021
OL,8,FCensus), but campaigners say the
OL,9,Fissues Sarah's facing aren't new ones.
OL,10,FAlex Harrison, Disability Wales'
OL,11,FDisability Equality Officer, says
OL,12,Fdisabled people often have to go
OL,13,Fwithout luxury on their wedding day,
OL,14,Fbut encounter many hurdles as a result.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
