OL,3,CBride-to-be to take bus to own wedding
OL,4,Cdue to lack of accessible transport
OL,6,F"We see it constantly. Organising a
OL,7,Fwedding is stressful enough without
OL,8,Fall these extra barriers to work
OL,9,Fthrough. I think there needs to be
OL,10,Fmore understanding and I think
OL,11,Fsuppliers and the wedding industry, as
OL,12,Fa whole, need to realise that disabled
OL,13,Fpeople like to get married too."
OL,15,FSarah says she doesn't expect special
OL,16,Ftreatment, but wishes more
OL,17,Fconsideration was given to support
OL,18,Fpeople like her. She emphasises that
OL,19,Fone size doesn't fit all.
