OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F461A1722380147
OL,3,CBride-to-be to take bus to own wedding
OL,4,Cdue to lack of accessible transport
OL,6,F"It's about being reasonable - having
OL,7,Freasonable adjustments and reasonable
OL,8,Fthings in place to make life easier
OL,9,Ffor not just one person, but for
OL,10,Feverybody. It's the small things that
OL,11,Fwe can change."
OL,13,FBut Sarah is determined to get to her
OL,14,Fwedding however she can and make the
OL,15,Fmost of her day.
OL,17,F"Whatever happens, there is absolutely
OL,18,Fno doubt that I'm going to have an
OL,19,Famazing day."
